Placeholder Recurring Encounter

Something happens! In the scary plains.

choices:

* Negotiate = Try to convince them
    @if check negotiation hard {
      You convince them!
      +heal_spirits medium
      +give_gold medium
    } @else {
      You fail!
      +rem_gold medium
      +damage_spirits medium
    }

* Fight = Do the ultimate punchies
    @if check combat medium {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits medium
        +give_gold medium
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +damage_health medium
        +damage_spirits medium
    }

* Sneak = Use big sneaky skills
    @if check cunning medium {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits medium
        +give_gold medium
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +damage_health medium
        +damage_spirits medium
    }
